# scoring-algorithms

The scoring system implements multi-faceted rating and ranking calculations across different sports:

## Player Rating System (Importance: 95/100)
- Dynamic rating adjustments based on:
  - Opponent strength factors
  - Match outcome weighting
  - Game score differentials
  - Historical performance trends
- Rating progression tracking with milestone achievements

## Division Standings Algorithm (Importance: 90/100)
- Complex ranking calculations incorporating:
  - Match win percentage
  - Game win percentage
  - Net points differential
  - Head-to-head records
- Dynamic division classification tiers

## Achievement System (Importance: 75/100)
- Rarity-based achievement tracking:
  - Common achievements
  - Rare achievements
  - Epic achievements  
  - Legendary achievements
- Progressive unlock mechanics tied to gameplay metrics
- Multi-tiered reward point allocation

## Sport-Specific Analytics (Importance: 85/100)
- Performance metric calculations customized by sport
- Court utilization analytics with benchmarks
- Player participation trending analysis
- Custom forfeit impact calculations

## Personal Statistics (Importance: 80/100)
- Multi-sport rating calculations
- Progressive milestone tracking
- Weighted performance metrics
- Form tracking across game types
- Streak calculations and classifications

